        embed_id: "9c73dc02-06bc-4837-804e-ee574d68766a",
        type: "event",
        content: "type: event_result\nid: \"314737625\"\nprovider: meetup\ntitle: \"HoA #74: \\\"CLAUDE.md\\\" — The One File That Makes AI Remember How You Work\"\ndescription: \"You open Claude. You explain your preferences. You get a decent result. Next session, you explain the same preferences again. And again. And again.\\n\\nThis is how most people work with AI: every session starts from zero. The model forgets who you are, what you care about, and how you want things done. So you compensate with longer prompts, more back-and-forth, and lower expectations.\\nOne file fixes this. It is called CLAUDE.md.\\n\\nIn this session, I will show you what CLAUDE.md is, what goes into it, and what you should keep out. You will leave this session knowing:\\n\\n* What CLAUDE.md does and where it lives in Claude Cowork\\n* The five sections that belong in every CLAUDE.md (and the three things that do not)\\n* How to write your first version in under 20 minutes\\n* Why CLAUDE.md is the foundation for everything else: Skills, connectors, and recurring workflows.\\n\\nThis Meetup is part of the launch week for my new Claude Cowork online course. The course covers the full system: Skills, evaluation, configuration, connectors, cost discipline, and bounded recurring workflows. If you want to go deeper after the session, the course will be available at a launch-week discount.\"\nurl: \"https://www.meetup.com/hands-on-agile-berlin-chapter-meetup/events/314737625/\"\ndate_start: \"2026-06-09T18:30:00+02:00\"\ndate_end: \"2026-06-09T19:30:00+02:00\"\ntimezone: Europe/Berlin\nevent_type: ONLINE\nvenue_name: Online event\nvenue_address: \"\"\nvenue_city: \"\"\nvenue_state: \"\"\nvenue_country: \"\"\nvenue_lat: -8.521147\nvenue_lon: 179.1962\norganizer_id: \"22469536\"\norganizer_name: Hands-on Agile Community\norganizer_slug: hands-on-agile-berlin-chapter-meetup\nrsvp_count: 69\nis_paid: false\nfee: null\nimage_url: \"https://secure.meetupstatic.com/photos/event/e/9/1/8/highres_472259672.jpeg\"\nhash: 31864497220f8a58\nembed_ref: hoa-74-claude-Tud\napp_id: events\nskill_id: search",
