        content: "type: event_result\nid: \"315051636\"\nprovider: meetup\ntitle: OpenClaw Anonymous Berlin #9\ndescription: \"Informal meetup for people interested in OpenClaw and AI agents.\\n\\nWe share what works/what doesn't and what we’re currently trying.\\n\\nFeel free to bring your laptop and half-working setup. We're all here to learn how to ride the tiger\\n\\n\\\\-\\\\-\\\\-\\\\-\\\\-\\\\-\\\\-\\\\-\\\\-\\\\-\\\\-\\\\-\\\\-\\\\-\\\\-\\\\-\\\\-\\\\-\\\\-\\nEvents usually unfold in two parts:\\n\\n1st part - People showcase projects, tools, setups and discuss learnings\\n\\n2nd part - Open discussion/networking\"\nurl: \"https://www.meetup.com/openclaw-anonymous-berlin/events/315051636/\"\ndate_start: \"2026-06-09T19:00:00+02:00\"\ndate_end: \"2026-06-09T21:00:00+02:00\"\ntimezone: Europe/Berlin\nevent_type: PHYSICAL\nvenue_name: w3.hub\nvenue_address: \"Möckernstraße 120, 10963 Berlin\"\nvenue_city: Berlin\nvenue_state: \"\"\nvenue_country: de\nvenue_lat: 52.497944\nvenue_lon: 13.380371\norganizer_id: \"38368211\"\norganizer_name: OpenClaw Anonymous Berlin\norganizer_slug: openclaw-anonymous-berlin\nrsvp_count: 18\nis_paid: false\nfee: null\nimage_url: \"https://secure.meetupstatic.com/photos/event/5/b/d/2/highres_532583506.jpeg\"\nhash: 86f0ae942be29ee3\nembed_ref: openclaw-anonymous-berlin-zrV\napp_id: events\nskill_id: search",
