        type: "event",
        content: "type: event_result\nid: \"2361991\"\nprovider: resident_advisor\ntitle: \"DUALISM WEEKENDER OPEN AIR & INDOOR  with GOAT BALL, HAKKE, silikon\"\ndescription: \"Lineup: Alliezz, alemiko, Amo (IT), Amøn, Athina, bbymeister, Balkhausen, Bitschu Batschu, brvder jakob, Carotin\\nGenres: Trance, Techno\\nDUALISM Weekender – one weekend, four floors. Open Air and indoor, four crews.\\n\\nTogether with GOAT BALL, SILIKON and HAKKE, we bring together different communities and scenes – not side by side, but within a shared space.\\n\\nFrom open air during the day to club formats at night, the programme ranges from fast-paced sounds to more experimental sets. Across the weekend, the floors run in parallel and overlap, featuring DJs, live acts, B2Bs and workshops.\\n\\nDUALISM stands for contrast – and that is exactly what this weekender is about: different scenes, one space.\"\nurl: \"https://ra.co/events/2361991\"\ndate_start: \"2026-06-05T22:00:00.000\"\ndate_end: \"2026-06-07T22:00:00.000\"\ntimezone: null\nevent_type: PHYSICAL\nvenue_name: \"://about blank\"\nvenue_address: \"Markgrafendamm 24c, 10245 Berlin, Germany\"\nvenue_city: Berlin\nvenue_state: null\nvenue_country: null\nvenue_lat: 53\nvenue_lon: 13\norganizer_name: GOAT BALL\norganizer_slug: null\norganizer_id: null\nrsvp_count: 2447\nis_paid: true\nfee: null\nimage_url: \"https://images.ra.co/a94611285b4f831cba8b58bfa0c5a8c8562734bc.jpg\"\nartists: Alliezz|alemiko|Amo (IT)|Amøn|Athina|bbymeister|Balkhausen|Bitschu Batschu|brvder jakob|Carotin\ngenres: Trance|Techno\nminimum_age: 18\nis_festival: false\nhash: deaa81aa774aec8f\nembed_ref: dualism-weekender-open-hLa\napp_id: events\nskill_id: search",
