        embed_id: "9683a88d-45af-45d9-b284-2fd0dc33efbd",
        type: "event",
        content: "type: event_result\nid: \"2353102\"\nprovider: resident_advisor\ntitle: FOREVER 25 curated by Peter Schumann & miAs\ndescription: \"Lineup: Jenner, Marc Romboy, Medha, Peter Schumann, Bo Irion, Renato Cohen, RYBA, Tal Fussman, AVA Irandoost, Babxi\\nGenres: Techno, Tech House\\nFOREVER 25 is our almost-monthly weekender: that means we run through from Friday night to Monday morning. It doesn't matter if you’re a Bar25 stammgast or with us for the first time – this is your chance to come early and stay long!\\n\\nFOREVER 25 also puts our residents in focus – this edition, Peter Schumann and miAs each curate a floor. Peter takes charge of Hopper: on Friday, a stellar techno lineup with Tal Fussman, Leipzig-based Medha and RYBA bringing the deep and dubby grooves. Saturday night is all about tech house: Peter himself warms up the floor together with Bo Irion, before Renate Cohen and Marc Romboy, and Toronto-based cornerstone of melodic techno, Jenner in the closing.\\n\\nmiAs’s party me:us, invites Joseph Disco, Kevin Bayer, Mary Quo and Vero Standke on Saturday night for some spacey bouncy minimal-tech madness.\\n\\nMeanwhile in Acid Bogen, we are excited to have a vocal deep house live set from French trio dOP, as well as beloved minimal house duo Jakob Seidensticker & Melina on Friday night. On Saturday night house and disco from Babxi, bouncy minimal house from LEENI & Danilo Kupfernagel, and a banging peak time set from our dear Franca.\\n\\nSunday ends with a bang: moving from Isabeau Fort’s light breezes and solid waves to bouncy and melodic tech house from Yamagucci, followed by Phunkadelica’s sparkling, multi-flavoured injection of grooves, timeless beats, and spicy snares and a closing set from JAMYN PHŌENIX extending late into the night.\\n\\nAlso watch out for Acid Bingo and Deeon’s Drag Show and plenty other surprises peppered throughout the weekend. 50+ hours of music and performances as old and new friends come together. See you on the dancefloor!\\n\\nLimited presale. More tickets are available at the club. A presale ticket does not guarantee entry, and the club reserves the right to refuse admission. In case of refusal, the ticket price will be refunded via RA (excluding fees).\\n\\n5€ re-entry fee may apply.\\n\\nPlease note that the non-smoking regulation...\"\nurl: \"https://ra.co/events/2353102\"\ndate_start: \"2026-06-05T22:00:00.000\"\ndate_end: \"2026-06-08T01:00:00.000\"\ntimezone: null\nevent_type: PHYSICAL\nvenue_name: Kater\nvenue_address: \"Holzmarktstrasse 25, 10243 Berlin\"\nvenue_city: Berlin\nvenue_state: null\nvenue_country: null\nvenue_lat: 52.511551\nvenue_lon: 13.426833\norganizer_name: Kater\norganizer_slug: null\norganizer_id: null\nrsvp_count: 406\nis_paid: true\nfee: null\nimage_url: \"https://images.ra.co/c820ea50f3f0419fe0720b8d1435c4d666a31653.jpg\"\nartists: Jenner|Marc Romboy|Medha|Peter Schumann|Bo Irion|Renato Cohen|RYBA|Tal Fussman|AVA Irandoost|Babxi\ngenres: Techno|Tech House\nminimum_age: null\nis_festival: false\nhash: b3c119660c2f776b\nembed_ref: forever-25-curated-ipv\napp_id: events\nskill_id: search",
