        content: "type: event_result\nid: \"2440884\"\nprovider: resident_advisor\ntitle: \"XTRUDE x MASS INVITES w/ Psyk, Setaoc Mass, ASEC live, Laure Croft, Jensen Interceptor\"\ndescription: \"Lineup: ASEC, Laure Croft, Mirella Kroes, Psyk, TONI BA, ValaV, Amor Satyr, Coco Cobra, Jensen Interceptor, Cirkle\\nPsyk is one of techno’s most distinctive contemporary voices, known for a sound that balances precision, depth and hypnotic intensity. Both as a DJ and producer, he moves fluidly between driving, functional techno and more stripped-back, atmospheric territory, always with a strong sense of control and refinement. Through acclaimed releases, immersive DJ sets and his influential Non Series imprint, Psyk has built a singular artistic identity rooted in subtle power and meticulous craftsmanship. Constantly evolving yet unmistakably his own, his approach continues to shape the deeper edges of modern techno. On Saturday, June 6th Psyk helms the ROBUS floor for XTRUDE and is joined by Laure Croft, ASEC live, and more while on the SUMME floor we host Jensen Interceptor, Amor Satyr, and Coco Cobra. During the day time on Sunday, Setaoc Mass hosts on the OPAN floor and invites Elise Massoni, Cirkle, Connor Wall and Neo.\\n\\nADDITIONAL INFO:\\n\\n• Cash and cashless payment\\n\\nDIRECTIONS:\\n\\n• Via S-Bahn - 4 stops from Ostkreuz or 3 stops from Neukölln and then a 5 minute walk from Schöneweide station.\\n\\n• Via Bus 165 - 18 minute ride from Schlesisches Tor to Obrikatstr. and then a 3 minute walk from the stop.\\n\\nONLINE PRESALE:\\n\\nPlease note that having a presale ticket does not assure admission. The club reserves the right to decline entry, with tickets being refunded accordingly. Please anticipate potential delays due to enhanced security checks at the entrance, even for ticket holders. Your cooperation and understanding are greatly appreciated. Thank you.\"\nurl: \"https://ra.co/events/2440884\"\ndate_start: \"2026-06-06T23:59:00.000\"\ndate_end: \"2026-06-08T08:00:00.000\"\ntimezone: null\nevent_type: PHYSICAL\nvenue_name: RSO.BERLIN\nvenue_address: \"Schnellerstrasse 137, 12439 Berlin\"\nvenue_city: Berlin\nvenue_state: null\nvenue_country: null\nvenue_lat: 52.45989\nvenue_lon: 13.50548\norganizer_name: RSO.BERLIN\norganizer_slug: null\norganizer_id: null\nrsvp_count: 815\nis_paid: true\nfee: null\nimage_url: \"https://images.ra.co/266447afb52ff2cfbfd2f700d1984e3d1a5d4aff.png\"\nartists: ASEC|Laure Croft|Mirella Kroes|Psyk|TONI BA|ValaV|Amor Satyr|Coco Cobra|Jensen Interceptor|Cirkle\ngenres: null\nminimum_age: 18\nis_festival: false\nhash: f64dd40e89341a17\nembed_ref: xtrude-x-mass-wbq\napp_id: events\nskill_id: search",
