        content: "type: event_result\nid: \"2448061\"\nprovider: resident_advisor\ntitle: \"One Year of [8] Afterparty with Aliar, Max Theodor, Liam Taj, Nyennea, Trademark\"\ndescription: \"Lineup: Aliar, Taylor Cherry, griefeater, Nyennea\\nGenres: House, Experimental\\nCelebrating a year-long journey leading to these exceptional events — bringing 60+ carefully selected artists across 7 stages during 20 continuous hours at 3 beloved locations.\\n\\nThe main event inside a historic factory complex with a hidden bunkers continue with a baroque-style Mitte-located afterparty alongside Hinterraum's Max Theodor & Liam Taj, GIFT's Trademark & queens of the place we can't pronounce — Aliar & Nyennea.\\n\\nPREPARTY (feat. DOPE) (2 stages / 17:00–22:30) [FREE ENTRY]\\n@ PAOLO PINKEL / Karl-Marx-Straße 55, 12043 Berlin\\n\\nMAIN EVENT (4 stages / 22:30–07:00) [RA TICKETS]\\n@ THE OLD FACTORY + BUNKERS / Greifswalder Str. 23A, 10405 Berlin\\n\\nAFTERPARTY (07:00–12:00) [€10 CASH]\\n@ BAR131 (COOP STUIDOS) / Chausseestraße 131A, 10115 Berlin\\n\\nMore information & updates: \\nINSTAGRAM @club8ing \\nWEB https//club8 .ing/\"\nurl: \"https://ra.co/events/2448061\"\ndate_start: \"2026-06-07T07:00:00.000\"\ndate_end: \"2026-06-07T12:30:00.000\"\ntimezone: null\nevent_type: PHYSICAL\nvenue_name: Bar131\nvenue_address: \"Chausseestraße 131A, 10115 Berlin, Germany\"\nvenue_city: Berlin\nvenue_state: null\nvenue_country: null\nvenue_lat: 53\nvenue_lon: 13\norganizer_name: \"[8]\"\norganizer_slug: null\norganizer_id: null\nrsvp_count: 4\nis_paid: true\nfee: null\nimage_url: \"https://images.ra.co/3170a683c6d081ae9666b776284054e7802a95bf.jpg\"\nartists: Aliar|Taylor Cherry|griefeater|Nyennea\ngenres: House|Experimental\nminimum_age: null\nis_festival: false\nhash: 902ec14170d7e432\nembed_ref: one-year-of-nlr\napp_id: events\nskill_id: search",
