        embed_id: "c670949e-2ada-444d-896d-bd5ffddd8c35",
        type: "event",
        content: "type: event_result\nid: \"315116867\"\nprovider: meetup\ntitle: AI trading agents. How to start?\ndescription: \"What are the best trading strategies for AI agents?\\n\\n**What we cover:**\\n\\n* when deterministic and rule-based strategies are still useful\\n* how AI agents can adapt to changing market conditions\\n* how Robonet's quant and MCP-style tools support strategy testing and deployment\\n* why reducing taker fees matters when thousands of agents are trading\\n* how limiting token usage and unnecessary tool calls can make AI trading more efficient\\n* what Eterna and Robonet could unlock together for agentic trading\\n\\nA practical conversation about how infrastructure can make AI agents more useful.\"\nurl: \"https://www.meetup.com/putting-ai-to-work/events/315116867/\"\ndate_start: \"2026-06-09T16:00:00+02:00\"\ndate_end: \"2026-06-09T17:00:00+02:00\"\ntimezone: Europe/Berlin\nevent_type: ONLINE\nvenue_name: Online event\nvenue_address: \"\"\nvenue_city: \"\"\nvenue_state: \"\"\nvenue_country: \"\"\nvenue_lat: -8.521147\nvenue_lon: 179.1962\norganizer_id: \"38487148\"\norganizer_name: Putting AI to work\norganizer_slug: putting-ai-to-work\nrsvp_count: 4\nis_paid: false\nfee: null\nimage_url: \"https://secure.meetupstatic.com/photos/event/a/4/2/2/highres_534582018.jpeg\"\nhash: 5b02dd8c1cb52de5\nembed_ref: ai-trading-agents-nXm\napp_id: events\nskill_id: search",
