        embed_id: "df18e8b1-d81f-41a3-8e9e-a05b14f41dc3",
        type: "event",
        content: "type: event_result\nid: \"315101332\"\nprovider: meetup\ntitle: AI Future-Club Init Event\ndescription: \"Enough watching from the sidelines. This event is for developers who want to get their hands dirty with AI, building, breaking, and figuring out what actually works **beyond the hype**.\\n\\nAt our kickoff, we're not doing intros and ice-breakers. We're diving straight into the conversation that matters: **what do we build, learn, and ship together?**\\nCome loaded with:\\n\\n* The AI problems you're actually trying to solve\\n* Tools or techniques you want to dig into as a group\\n* Wild ideas for projects, hacks, or experiments we could tackle\\n\\nThis is your chance to help set the direction before it's set for you.\\n\\nBefore you arrive, **sign up for our newsletter** to stay in the loop on session recaps, resources, and upcoming events: [Future-Club](https://future-club.org)\\n\\nShow up ready to contribute. 🔥 See you there! 👋\\n\\n***Late addition, a group member will also be demoing a recent AI project.***\"\nurl: \"https://www.meetup.com/hfberlin/events/315101332/\"\ndate_start: \"2026-06-11T18:00:00+02:00\"\ndate_end: \"2026-06-11T20:00:00+02:00\"\ntimezone: Europe/Berlin\nevent_type: PHYSICAL\nvenue_name: TBD\nvenue_address: Berlin\nvenue_city: Berlin\nvenue_state: \"\"\nvenue_country: de\nvenue_lat: 52.52076\nvenue_lon: 13.409428\norganizer_id: \"19112396\"\norganizer_name: Hackers / Founders Berlin\norganizer_slug: hfberlin\nrsvp_count: 14\nis_paid: false\nfee: null\nimage_url: \"https://secure.meetupstatic.com/photos/event/a/0/e/6/highres_534581190.jpeg\"\nhash: 4fe5cc8ab1b2787f\nembed_ref: ai-future-club-XOk\napp_id: events\nskill_id: search",
