        embed_id: "70d5034d-a908-47e2-a697-f4ad34ce079a",
        type: "event",
        content: "type: event_result\nid: \"2371122\"\nprovider: resident_advisor\ntitle: \"FREE OPEN AIR: KINDER DER WELT 'BACKYARD' FEATURING VIMANA with MARKET & EXHIBITION\"\ndescription: \"Lineup: Maque, Venus Melissa, BECCA SORANA, Rafael\\nGenres: Trance, Techno\\nKINDERDERWELT is very excited to bring back the new edition of Lokschuppen's \\\"BACKYARD\\\" - Free Open Air + Market & Exhibition - format back for another year!\\n\\nFor the market, the focus is on showcasing independent artists and designers across disciplines — from fashion and painting to tattooing, up-cycling, jewelry, illustration, and more. Unlike traditional flea markets, this project is not about second-hand reselling, but about giving space to original, self-produced work and connecting creators with an engaged audience.   \\n\\nEach date, the courtyard transforms into a creative platform — with 10–15 artist booths, one exhibition, a club-hosted bar, and a stage reserved for a collective showcase. The vibe is casual but considered: a blend of exhibition, art market, open-air hangout, and Berlin subculture.\\n\\nThis market is a collaboration with @___vimana___ collective, where they will bring their unique sound to our backyard. \"\nurl: \"https://ra.co/events/2371122\"\ndate_start: \"2026-06-07T12:00:00.000\"\ndate_end: \"2026-06-07T21:00:00.000\"\ntimezone: null\nevent_type: PHYSICAL\nvenue_name: Lokschuppen Berlin\nvenue_address: \"Warschauer Brücke, Revaler Straße 99 Zugang über, 10245 Berlin, Germany\"\nvenue_city: Berlin\nvenue_state: null\nvenue_country: null\nvenue_lat: 52.507473\nvenue_lon: 13.452055\norganizer_name: Lokschuppen Berlin\norganizer_slug: null\norganizer_id: null\nrsvp_count: 68\nis_paid: true\nfee_amount: \"0\"\nfee_currency: EUR\nimage_url: \"https://images.ra.co/9a6e8e091a675af0d92412bd41abba56d28b9f2b.png\"\nartists: Maque|Venus Melissa|BECCA SORANA|Rafael\ngenres: Trance|Techno\nminimum_age: 18\nis_festival: false\nhash: 9f27c0b3c7357485\nembed_ref: free-open-air-Uy7\napp_id: events\nskill_id: search",
