        content: "type: event_result\nid: \"2416637\"\nprovider: resident_advisor\ntitle: Dirty Trancing - Open Air\ndescription: \"Lineup: DJ Hyperfck, Pamela Rave\\nGenres: Trance\\nSummer’s around the corner and we’re serving the best feelings with it: sun glistening on your face while eating the juiciest watermelon of the year — all while sparkling trance music pumps across the dancefloor next to the Spree. \\n\\nSounds like the open air season opener everyone’s been waiting for?\\n\\nGet your tickets now, this is the cherry you‘d better start picking soon!\\n\\naddress: Vor dem Schlesischen Tor 2, 10997 Berlin – just keep walking towards the Inselgarten next to the water\"\nurl: \"https://ra.co/events/2416637\"\ndate_start: \"2026-06-07T15:00:00.000\"\ndate_end: \"2026-06-07T22:00:00.000\"\ntimezone: null\nevent_type: PHYSICAL\nvenue_name: Freischwimmer\nvenue_address: \"Vor dem Schlesischen Tor 2a, 10997 Berlin\"\nvenue_city: Berlin\nvenue_state: null\nvenue_country: null\nvenue_lat: 52.49744\nvenue_lon: 13.452179\norganizer_name: Dirty Trancing\norganizer_slug: null\norganizer_id: null\nrsvp_count: 101\nis_paid: true\nfee_amount: \"15\"\nfee_currency: EUR\nimage_url: \"https://images.ra.co/9010a2846c75a69935544b5f7272cabe486594fd.png\"\nartists: DJ Hyperfck|Pamela Rave\ngenres: Trance\nminimum_age: 18\nis_festival: false\nhash: b57b88046794cc21\nembed_ref: dirty-trancing-open-i7j\napp_id: events\nskill_id: search",
