        type: "event",
        content: "type: event_result\nid: \"2427765\"\nprovider: resident_advisor\ntitle: \"U10247: A seasick Sunday in Berlin (feat. maniac&me and Guyrot) ...Free Entry\"\ndescription: \"Lineup: maniac&me\\nGenres: Minimal, Deep House\\nU10247 delivers the cure for another seasick Sunday in Berlin - catch the vibe and meet the maniac and Guyrot for an e-healing session at Minimal Bar!\\n\\nGuyrot is a Berlin-based electronic music producer and DJ. He has released music on labels such as Satya, Heisenberg, Zapped Records, Perception Records, Ultra Nights etc…\\nGuyrot drifts between raw minimalism, house and techno, infused with elements of dub, acid, soul, and hip hop.\\n\\nmaniac&me will anticipate the energy with his signature sound containing deep tech, dub and progressive tunes, always in order to get hearts and hips swinging: No dancing, no paradise!\\n\\nNachtflug Widerstand stands strong with the Minimal Bar values:\\nNo Racism. No Sexism. No Homophobia. No Transphobia. No Discrimination of any kind.\"\nurl: \"https://ra.co/events/2427765\"\ndate_start: \"2026-06-07T18:00:00.000\"\ndate_end: \"2026-06-08T04:00:00.000\"\ntimezone: null\nevent_type: PHYSICAL\nvenue_name: Minimal Bar\nvenue_address: Rigaer Strasse 31; Friedrichshain; 10247 Berlin; Germany\nvenue_city: Berlin\nvenue_state: null\nvenue_country: null\nvenue_lat: 52.51639\nvenue_lon: 13.46406\norganizer_name: mini.mal elektrokneipe\norganizer_slug: null\norganizer_id: null\nrsvp_count: 35\nis_paid: false\nfee: null\nimage_url: \"https://images.ra.co/76e569399e32abb2f590342987808045f878e355.png\"\nartists: maniac&me\ngenres: Minimal|Deep House\nminimum_age: 21\nis_festival: false\nhash: 0990128dbf4b9735\nembed_ref: u10247-a-seasick-8Q6\napp_id: events\nskill_id: search",
