        embed_id: "0bb8c4f2-540e-49be-ba44-b527a059b614",
        type: "event",
        content: "type: event_result\nid: \"2381610\"\nprovider: resident_advisor\ntitle: Massive Attack live\ndescription: \"Lineup: Massive Attack\\nMassive Attack will perform at Zitadelle Spandau \\n\\nThis year, the British band is finally set to release new music:\\nAs Massive Attack announced on their social media channels at the end of 2025, several new songs they have been working on recently will be released in 2026.\\n“The tracks will be available physically and digitally through a new label.” However, Spotify is expressly excluded.\\nThat’s for sure: their live shows have been thrilling audiences for decades. With their powerful band, impressive visuals, and rotating guest vocalists, it's well worth seeing Massive Attack live in June at their only German show at the Zitadelle Spandau\\n\\n07.06.2026 – Berlin, Zitadelle  \\n\\nTicket prices: 73,00 Euro plus fees\\nTickets available exclusively at eventim.de\\n\"\nurl: \"https://ra.co/events/2381610\"\ndate_start: \"2026-06-07T19:00:00.000\"\ndate_end: \"2026-06-07T22:00:00.000\"\ntimezone: null\nevent_type: PHYSICAL\nvenue_name: Zitadelle Spandau\nvenue_address: \"Am Juliusturm 64, 13599 Berlin\"\nvenue_city: Berlin\nvenue_state: null\nvenue_country: null\nvenue_lat: 53\nvenue_lon: 13\norganizer: null\nrsvp_count: 149\nis_paid: true\nfee_amount: \"86,05\"\nfee_currency: EUR\nimage_url: \"https://images.ra.co/e1d9b1147b14ae249a9ed41e47cd10b47f4d90e0.jpg\"\nartists: Massive Attack\ngenres: null\nminimum_age: null\nis_festival: false\nhash: 5e94ba396c3186cc\nembed_ref: massive-attack-live-6W7\napp_id: events\nskill_id: search",
